+| Event | backoffLevel after | Window |
+|---|---|---|
+| First rate-limit hit | 0 | 15 min |
+| Probe dispatched (window elapsed) | 1 | — |
+| Probe returns rate-limited | 1 | 30 min |
+| Probe dispatched again | 2 | — |
+| Probe returns rate-limited | 2 | 60 min (capped) |
